name: Miitopia by Bulbasaur 9
description:
Miitopia is one of Bulbasaur 9's cover artworks morphed in to glitch funk by Hulki Okan Tabak.

Bulbasaur 9 is an emerging kid artist and an avid YouTuber on https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRjLXhHKyBpI813vFvMiMVQ.

This is a part of our long lasting father son collaboration series between Hulki Okan Tabak and Bulbasaur 9 - now for the first time on HEN.

Minted on HEN, October 2021
